parameters: \n<Aaron>You were right...I guess it wasn’t so safe after all...
\n<Audrey>...It wasn't your fault. He clearly shouldn't be
jumping on it, just like you said.
\n<Aaron>Right...But I can't help but to feel responsible
\n<Audrey>Now that I think about it was kinda funny.
\n<Audrey>Crap, I could have taken a picture of him.
\n<Audrey>Sorry for being such a drag sometimes.
\n<Audrey>You must be sick of me already.
\n<Audrey>But really, thank you. Without you guys, I wouldn’t
\n<Aaron>C'mon! Why not? They will totally accept you.
\n<Aaron>What? What is so complicated about it?
\n<Aaron>Oh...I'm sorry... I didn't mean to... is it so
\n<Audrey>It is, actually. Didn’t I tell you?
\n<Aaron>Okay, maybe you won't be able to leave the town
but...you could study here, right? It's not exactly
what you were looking for but...
\n<Aaron>I don't know the whole story, but you have to keep--
